    "The authors look at factors like weather, traffic, and road conditions to see how they influence risky driving events.",
    "They use machine learning to analyze a large dataset and identify the most important contextual factors.",
    "Their findings suggest that context significantly impacts risk and could be used to create a new insurance scheme based on driving location ('Pay-where-you-drive').",
